snippet: Although there was nothing encouraging to report about the offensive linemen Chris Snee and David Baas, cornerback Corey Webster said he would play Sunday.
abstract: NFL Roundup; New York Giants injury report, listing 15 players, provides mixed news for team, including announcement that cornerback Corey Webster will return to play in upcoming game against Philadelphia Eagles; other football news noted.
lead_paragraph: Although there was nothing encouraging to report about the offensive linemen Chris Snee and David Baas, cornerback Corey Webster said he would play Sunday.
